description.p:
13g of curing agent is weighed, added with 20g of water, O.lg of wetting agent and 0.2g of dispersant, and then stirred;

after stirring for 20 minutes, O.lg of dispersant, O.lg of defoamer, and 0.3g of bentonite are added to the system, and continuously stirred for 15 minutes;

7g of talcum powder is added, stirred for 5 minutes, added with 4g of barite, 7g of iron oxide red and 0.2g of defoamer, and then stirred for 15 minutes.

0.03g of modified graphene is added and dispersed for 20 minutes;

215.2g of zinc powder and 40g of water are added to ensure the wetting of the system;

60g of epoxy resin is added and dispersed for 15 minutes.
